<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">);</span></span></code></pre></div><h4 id="_8-2-deriving-role-pda" tabindex="-1">8.2 Deriving Role PDA <a class="header-anchor" href="#_8-2-deriving-role-pda" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;8.2 Deriving Role PDA&quot;">​</a></h4><p><strong>Seed Values:</strong></p><ul><li>Literal: &quot;profile-role&quot;</li><li>Profile public key</li><li>Role sequence ID (as little‑endian byte array)</li></ul><p><strong>Sample Code:</strong></p><div class="language-tsx vp-adaptive-theme"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">tsx</span><pre class="shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark vp-code" tabindex="0"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">const</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;"> roleSeqId</span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;"> =</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;"> 0</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">; </span><span style="--shiki-light:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D;">// or the current value from the profile account</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">const</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;"> [</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">rolePda</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">, </span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">roleBump</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">] </span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">=</span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;"> await</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;"> web3.PublicKey.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;">findProgramAddress</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">(</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">  [</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">    Buffer.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;">from</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;profile-role&quot;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">),</span></span>
